metadata.name: Bypass Canal
metadata.description:
St. Petersburg.  City detail.  On the Obvodny Canal in the area of ​​the Alexander Nevsky Lavra.  An unnamed road bridge over an artificial canal.

On this frame there are natural highlights of the film.
Without the use of compositing and photoshop. Film frame scanned in the highest resolution.
